{
  "stem": "8370.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "After a few minutes, Irma Grese came out, walked around, collected the leash of her dog from a SS man who was keeping the dog for the time being.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Then I saw the tins of Zyklon B.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It was a poison.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It was a gravel, green gravel.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They put that in the ventilator all around, close the ventilator.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "The action was completed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We heard the ventilator working after a couple of minutes to give fresh air to the gas chamber.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Because now, the Sonderkommando, which I told before, have to walk in, take the corpses, put into the oven, and burn them.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And so it was the little, innocent children have been finished.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "It was a question of couple of minutes.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So it was like that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I know that Irma Grese was arrested after, condemned to death.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But it was, thanks God, in the English occupation zone.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And apparently, the death sentence was executed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, to a certain extent, yes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Of course, it was very secret, very secret.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There have been two kinds of resistance movements.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "One, I was not involved in.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was collecting and passing information from the camp to the outside world.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "This way, for example, have been sent outside the camp, photographs taken by Dawid Warszawski from the roof of one of the barracks.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He was covering the barracks, you see, with a, the special bitumen paint.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And Dawid had done the photographs.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He collected-- he find a camera through this, what I told you, Canada, from the warehouse, and used this camera.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And these photograph was sent outside.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Birkenau.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In Birkenau, from the roof of one of the barracks next to the crematorium number four.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they got their people, naked women, before the entrance to the gas chamber.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
